blueprint.label: Nuclear (2.4GW) and Uranium Processing
blueprint.description:
BOTS CAN'T PLACE A COUPLE RAILS FOR WATER. DO IT BY HAND.

Generates 2.4GW and enough fuel cells for ~650 more reactors (i.e. 9 of the 10GW layout) plus some nuclear train fuel.

Water comes via tanker but pumping directly into the station tanks is also an option.

The reactor comes from
https://factorioprints.com/view/-M8JPYKBgXXIuHNXu-3X
with no changes other than the power default "on".

Kovarex is my own.
